### 📈 預防措施
- **前後端同步檢查機制**:
  ```javascript
  // 自動化前後端消息類型同步檢查
  class MessageTypeValidator {
      constructor() {
          this.frontendTypes = new Set();
          this.backendTypes = new Set();
      }
      
      registerFrontendType(type) {
          this.frontendTypes.add(type);
      }
      
      registerBackendType(type) {
          this.backendTypes.add(type);
      }
      
      validateSync() {
          const frontendOnly = [...this.frontendTypes].filter(type => !this.backendTypes.has(type));
          const backendOnly = [...this.backendTypes].filter(type => !this.frontendTypes.has(type));
          
          if (frontendOnly.length > 0) {
              console.warn(`前端專有消息類型: ${frontendOnly.join(', ')}`);
          }
          
          if (backendOnly.length > 0) {
              console.warn(`後端專有消息類型: ${backendOnly.join(', ')}`);
          }
          
          return frontendOnly.length === 0 && backendOnly.length === 0;
      }
  }
  ```

- **規則更新**: 
  - `.cursor/rules/websocket_rules.mdc` - 添加消息類型同步檢查要求
